  "texts": [
    "(A) Binary postoperative complication prediction using KNN; (B) to (E) multilabel mechanical ventilation duration prediction (I: 0-12 h, II: 12-24 h, III: 24-48 h, and IV: >48 h) using KNN, respectively; (F) binary postoperative complication prediction using KNN+LR; (G) to (J) multilabel mechanical ventilation duration prediction (I: 0-12 h, II: 12-24 h, III: 24-48 h, and IV: >48 h) using KNN+LR, respectively.",
